# Structure

## 4 types of functions

 - Paths
 - Scalar Value Functions
 - Vector Fields
 - Vector Functions


## For each one

 - Definition
 - Equivalent ways of defining
 - Getting accustomed to them
 - Geometric Interpretations
 - Calculus:
     - Derivetives
     - Geometric Interpretations of derivetives, what types of functions they give, etc.
     - Theorems of derivetives
     - Integrals
     - Geometric Interpretations of integrals, what types of functions they give, etc.
     - Theorems of integrals


